{"tid":999064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「超巨大黑影」在半山腰移動！美驚現「大腳怪」蹤跡　山腳下也能清楚看到","createTime":"2019-01-28T12:25:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-28T13:08:01.000Z","uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"837de8acf9430e304ef486e9978e3fd49af1e58a","tid":999064,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T12:25:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3867/3867769.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3867%2F3867769.jpg&h=ee0ce051&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲大腳怪現身山林。（圖／翻攝自YouTube／Austin M. Craig）<br />\n&nbsp;國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n美國加州在1958年時發現「大腳怪（Sasquatch）」的超大腳印，也因此受到大家的關注。近日一名美國猶他州的男子奧斯汀（Austin Craig）表示，他在本月2日於當地城市普若佛（Provo）東北邊的山腳下，發現了一個又大又黑的身影，看起來像人又像是一隻身形高大的動物，跟傳說中的著名「大腳怪」有許多相似之處。<br />\n根據外媒報導，在羅傑（Roger Patterson） 和包柏（Bob Gilmlin）在53年前，首次聲稱拍到大腳怪的身影之後，本月2日，又有住在美國猶他州普若佛的居民發現了這個巨大而陌生的「人物」。<br />\n其中一名目擊者奧斯汀表示，他跟朋友當時正潛伏在山坡上的一顆岩石上，注意到遠方出現一個用有明顯高聳身材的「人」，並且在匆忙中認為這應該就是傳說中的「大腳怪」；他用相機將看到的場景照下，還將鏡頭不斷拉近，從影像中可以發現有一個巨大的黑色身影正在山上緩慢移動。<br />\n奧斯汀說，在看到這個影像後，他在朋友的陪同之下，回到拍攝地點去尋找有可能留下的大腳印或是毛皮，但是空手而歸；或許這個身影只是一隻熊，也有可能是一個人，甚至是其他東西，不過他依舊認為自己看到了大腳怪。<br />\n報導中指出，猶他州多年來頻頻傳出有人目擊到大腳怪的事件，也因此該州擁有一個致力於追捕野獸的部門，不過經過裡頭「大腳怪」組織的調查，對於這次的目擊事件尚無定論。<br />\n「大腳怪」在1958年，以美國原住民民間傳說的形象，首次被媒體聚焦，當時一名男子傑瑞（Jerry Crew）聲稱，他在北加州的一條溪附近發現屬於大腳怪的超大腳印。<br />\n▼影片取自YouTube，如遭刪除請見諒。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UnMxHBM75T4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUnMxHBM75T4&d=V%2FMePAjw%2FzabXJhWRsrUTDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=06260caa\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UnMxHBM75T4</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190128/1367289.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190128%2F1367289.htm&d=V%2FMePAjw%2FzabXJhWRsrUTDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=0b8dfc3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190128/1367289.htm</a>"},{"pid":"65ab6ebd15fff637e5b717e2ad1d8ed36d2c7ddd","tid":999064,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T12:27:15.000Z","msg":"同尼斯湖水怪一樣搵極都搵唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08b4509e8f10c0b7188096301b946f49bfe51b52","tid":999064,"uid":119330,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"65ab6ebd15fff637e5b717e2ad1d8ed36d2c7ddd","tid":999064,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T12:27:15.000Z","msg":"同尼斯湖水怪一樣搵極都搵唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T12:28:54.000Z","msg":"同尼斯湖水怪一樣<br />\n需要佢既時候 就會出現<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6534706152ae76da168cf52aeb458ddee48c427f","tid":999064,"uid":31254,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T12:29:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fdmsnrh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFdmsnrh.png&h=9c5a8dc3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d2444ddbc5757bfc2dc8648acc2a0613e6023e5e","tid":999064,"uid":1655,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T12:31:47.000Z","msg":"長毛睇完應該即刻爆血管"},{"pid":"1d39bbad73d551ebe50392ed310c50f69794a3a1","tid":999064,"uid":32577,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T12:41:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A0wHbox.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA0wHbox.jpg&h=9b55cfbc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bb699201b12415fc02f721270e8aec6366a5d063","tid":999064,"uid":157831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2444ddbc5757bfc2dc8648acc2a0613e6023e5e","tid":999064,"uid":1655,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T12:31:47.000Z","msg":"長毛睇完應該即刻爆血管"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T12:42:59.000Z","msg":"<